Package: pipeboard
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: xclip | xsel | wl-clipboard
Description: Cross-platform clipboard CLI with SSH + S3 sync
 Pipeboard is a command-line tool for managing clipboard operations with
 advanced features including:
  * Copy and paste text to/from clipboard
  * SSH peer-to-peer clipboard synchronization
  * S3 backend for remote clipboard storage
  * Clipboard history with search and recall
  * Image clipboard support (PNG)
  * Transform clipboard content with custom commands
  * Slot-based clipboard management
 .
 Pipeboard works seamlessly across Linux (X11/Wayland), macOS, and Windows.
